title: The New PlayStation Handheld Is Lame
description:
The PlayStation Portal doesn’t look great, or amazing, or even good, but even still, there’s some excitement to be had about a new Sony handheld, right? I mean, a portable PS5, in some capacity might be pretty cool?

Wrong!

This is a disaster.

And today, I’m gonna, talk about that.
